00:15:28.800 --> 00:15:30.070
so don't ever say that again.

00:15:30.370 --> 00:15:33.000
- Or else I'll get mad.
- Come here, give me a smooch.

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:35.240
Hey, stop it! That's disgusting!

00:15:43.650 --> 00:15:46.280
Looks like our Seo Rin
is keeping Father happy.

00:15:51.320 --> 00:15:53.120
Debt of gratitude?
What are you talking about?

00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:56.360
Your kindness is as vast as a river.

00:15:56.690 --> 00:15:59.760
Thanks to you, Chairman,
we could afford Hong Ju's tuition,

00:15:59.760 --> 00:16:02.600
and she was able to attend college.
And that's not all, is it?

00:16:02.830 --> 00:16:04.370
She even got a job at the hotel...

00:16:04.900 --> 00:16:06.240
and was sent abroad for training.

00:16:07.300 --> 00:16:11.080
I worry about
how we can ever repay you, Chairman.

00:16:11.910 --> 00:16:15.380
Hong Ju will be the pigeon
that brings you good fortune,

00:16:15.710 --> 00:16:17.080
so just you wait and see, Chairman.

00:16:17.580 --> 00:16:21.090
- Mom, it's a swallow, not a pigeon.
- What?

00:16:22.350 --> 00:16:25.360
Pigeon, swallow, what's the difference?

00:16:30.860 --> 00:16:32.560
Yeom San Wol, what are you doing here?

00:16:33.130 --> 00:16:34.330
Oh, my, CEO Chae.

00:16:35.700 --> 00:16:36.800
You're home now?

00:16:37.630 --> 00:16:40.270
- You must be tired.
- Assistant Manager Jin...

00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.410
came by to say hello.

00:16:41.540 --> 00:16:43.870
You should've told me you were coming.

00:16:44.210 --> 00:16:47.240
That way, I could have had the housekeeper
prepare a proper dinner for you.

00:16:47.310 --> 00:16:50.150
I'm sorry. It was a last-minute trip,

00:16:50.410 --> 00:16:52.320
so I didn't get a chance to inform you,
CEO Chae.

00:16:52.380 --> 00:16:56.290
I worried it would be rude to wait longer
to pay our respects to Chairman,

00:16:56.350 --> 00:16:58.020
so I was the one who insisted we come now.

00:16:58.320 --> 00:17:01.290
- That's why she came unannounced.
- That's not it.

00:17:01.830 --> 00:17:03.190
I told them to come.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:05.200
Pardon?

00:17:05.200 --> 00:17:08.100
Does she need your permission
just to come and say hello to me?

00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:11.900
Don't make our guests uncomfortable.
What's wrong with you?

00:17:13.370 --> 00:17:17.570
By the way, what did you think
of Chef Kang Jun Ho from earlier?

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:19.640
Chef Kang Jun Ho?

00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:21.710
Apparently, he's a very popular star chef.

00:17:21.710 --> 00:17:23.580
Our Hong Ju...

00:17:23.610 --> 00:17:25.950
was instrumental in recruiting him.

00:17:26.320 --> 00:17:28.990
He's the talent who won first place
in an American cooking competition, right?

00:17:29.120 --> 00:17:32.360
Yes. King Restaurant
was trying to scout him,

00:17:32.460 --> 00:17:34.020
but I managed to snatch him up first.

00:17:34.290 --> 00:17:38.160
I recommended him to CEO Chae
as head chef for Chang Restaurant.

00:17:38.330 --> 00:17:41.970
That sneaky little fox.
She went over my head to talk to Father.

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:44.640
Look at you.
You've really pulled something off.

00:17:46.570 --> 00:17:48.640
He's a talent
we just couldn't afford to lose.

00:17:48.710 --> 00:17:51.940
He's not officially on board yet,
so let's not get ahead of ourselves.

00:17:52.140 --> 00:17:55.210
We'll see how good he really is
over the next two months.

00:18:05.060 --> 00:18:08.530
- Get Seo Rin in here right now.
- What? Seo Rin?

00:18:09.090 --> 00:18:10.260
What has she done?

00:18:20.840 --> 00:18:22.440
Did Seo Rin get into trouble again?

00:18:23.210 --> 00:18:26.310
She's been quiet for a while.
What did she do the minute she got back?

00:18:34.920 --> 00:18:36.820
- Yes, CEO Chae.
- What have you been doing?

00:18:36.990 --> 00:18:38.060
Is something wrong?

00:18:38.090 --> 00:18:41.060
Get to the club, find Seo Rin,
and bring her here. Right now.

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:44.230
- The club?
- Didn't I say to watch her social media?

00:18:44.730 --> 00:18:46.830
Why didn't you listen to me
and let this happen?

00:18:47.500 --> 00:18:49.770
Go drag her here this instant. Now!

00:18:51.540 --> 00:18:52.640
That little brat.

00:18:53.240 --> 00:18:55.270
She was quiet for a while,
but she's at it again.

00:19:02.010 --> 00:19:05.520
Suk Hee likes the cake.
Tae Pyung bought it.

00:19:06.620 --> 00:19:08.750
Suk Hee, do you like the cake that much?

00:19:09.120 --> 00:19:10.290
Cake is good.

00:19:10.820 --> 00:19:14.260
Bok Gil is good too. You have some too.

00:19:14.730 --> 00:19:16.460
Jang Mi, you eat up.

00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:20.600
- What about me?
- Hey, you.

00:19:20.600 --> 00:19:23.300
Mom, I'm the one who bought it,
and you're not going to offer me any?

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:25.970
Tae Pyung, thank you.

00:19:26.970 --> 00:19:29.770
Seriously.
Why are you treating Mom like that?

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:32.180
Look at you. She's my mom too. So what?

00:19:32.440 --> 00:19:35.510
- Come here.
- Dad! Make him stop!

00:19:35.580 --> 00:19:38.780
- The frosting is yummy. Don't fight.
- Bring it on.

00:19:38.850 --> 00:19:40.350
- Leave Jang Mi alone.
- That's enough.

00:19:40.420 --> 00:19:42.350
- Go on, try me.
- Stop fooling around.

00:19:42.420 --> 00:19:44.860
- Go on.
- No, don't.

00:19:44.920 --> 00:19:45.920
Stop it.

00:19:47.120 --> 00:19:50.260
What? They expect you to double sales
in two months?

00:19:50.930 --> 00:19:53.900
- That's insane.
- What kind of restaurant does that?

00:19:54.330 --> 00:19:56.900
The clientele for fine dining restaurants
is pretty fixed,

00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:59.300
so doubling sales that fast is impossible.

00:19:59.300 --> 00:20:00.600
Does the CEO of Dream Hotel...

00:20:00.670 --> 00:20:02.440
have it out for you or something?

00:20:02.970 --> 00:20:06.240
Otherwise, how could anyone expect you
to double sales so suddenly?

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:09.410
- Don't worry about it.
- What? You think you can do it?

00:20:10.610 --> 00:20:12.280
That's my brother for you.

00:20:13.050 --> 00:20:15.020
That's right. He is my son, after all.

00:20:15.290 --> 00:20:17.720
- He's my son.
- Oh, please.

00:20:18.860 --> 00:20:20.990
By the way, honey, didn't you say...

00:20:21.060 --> 00:20:22.960
you were working on a joint project
with Dream Hotel?

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:23.960
Yes.

00:20:24.060 --> 00:20:27.800
I think I might get a chance
to meet that CEO soon.

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:30.700
I'm going to find out what her deal is.
The nerve of that lady.

00:20:30.770 --> 00:20:33.170
- How dare she treat my son like that?
- Please don't say anything.

00:20:34.570 --> 00:20:35.970
I'll handle my own affairs.

00:20:43.710 --> 00:20:47.580
- Just a second.
- My goodness. Look at you.

00:20:49.020 --> 00:20:50.190
Oh, Grandpa.

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:52.420
- My grandpa!
- Goodness.

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:54.960
How much did you have to drink?

00:20:55.030 --> 00:20:57.790
You're going to ruin your health.
You hear me?

00:20:58.800 --> 00:21:02.830
Just a little.
I was in such a good mood today.

00:21:03.100 --> 00:21:05.900
- So I had a few drinks.
- For goodness' sake.

00:21:06.070 --> 00:21:08.270
She said she was meeting some friends
she hadn't seen in a while.

00:21:08.670 --> 00:21:10.770
Looks like she had a few drinks
with them, Father.

00:21:10.810 --> 00:21:14.080
- Get her upstairs so she can rest.
- Yes, Father.

00:21:14.480 --> 00:21:17.310
- Goodness. Good night.
- Good night.

00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:20.150
My stomach burns.

00:21:26.560 --> 00:21:29.160
You deleted that photo from her socials,
didn't you?

00:21:29.530 --> 00:21:31.460
- Yes, ma'am.
- You should've handled it...

00:21:31.460 --> 00:21:33.560
before the PR Team
or Secretary Kim found out.

00:21:34.430 --> 00:21:36.770
Make sure this doesn't happen again.
Keep a close eye on her.

00:21:37.430 --> 00:21:39.800
Most young people
are on social media these days.

00:21:40.170 --> 00:21:41.300
I'm not sure we need to be this strict...

00:21:41.370 --> 00:21:43.910
Do you think I'd be cracking down
if she used it properly?

00:21:44.270 --> 00:21:46.840
But she only ever does things
that hurt our stock price.

00:21:48.710 --> 00:21:52.620
It's like Ma Seo Rin goes out of her way
just to mess with me.

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:54.250
Just like you'd expect from her bloodline.

00:21:54.920 --> 00:21:56.020
CEO Chae.

00:21:58.060 --> 00:21:59.060
You may go.

00:22:00.020 --> 00:22:01.930
I'll pay more attention from now on.

00:22:02.690 --> 00:22:03.890
Please try not to be so upset.

00:22:10.930 --> 00:22:13.470
Should I have taken
the other twin back then?

00:22:14.100 --> 00:22:15.940
Why is she becoming such a handful?

00:22:16.740 --> 00:22:18.240
She was so obedient when she was little.

00:22:35.760 --> 00:22:36.760
Mom.

00:22:37.630 --> 00:22:38.660
I love you.

00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:41.260
My beautiful mom.

00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:51.440
If my dear Jung Suk Hee wants
a whipped cream cake,

00:22:51.740 --> 00:22:53.310
then a whipped cream cake she'll have.

00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:55.350
Jung Suk Hee.

00:22:56.580 --> 00:22:58.650
Why does that name sound so familiar?

00:23:01.520 --> 00:23:04.120
Jung Suk Hee, where are you?

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:05.960
Jung Suk Hee, where are you?

00:23:06.320 --> 00:23:09.230
Where are you? Where is Jung Suk Hee?

00:23:10.360 --> 00:23:12.200
What? Did she overhear everything?

00:23:13.200 --> 00:23:16.730
Is that why she caught on and ran away?
Jung Suk Hee!

00:23:17.430 --> 00:23:20.040
Consider today the day
you and your children die.

00:23:20.270 --> 00:23:23.610
Where are you? Jung Suk Hee!

00:23:23.870 --> 00:23:25.440
Jung Suk Hee!

00:23:26.080 --> 00:23:27.240
Jung Suk Hee...

00:23:29.210 --> 00:23:31.380
How could I have forgotten that name?

00:23:31.950 --> 00:23:33.320
Even after all these years.

00:23:36.690 --> 00:23:39.220
- Let's go!
- Let go of me!

00:23:39.290 --> 00:23:44.060
- Take me to Jang Mi.
- Let go!

00:23:44.060 --> 00:23:46.700
- I said let go!
- Take me to Jang Mi.

00:23:46.700 --> 00:23:50.470
- Let's go!
- Let go of me!

00:23:57.040 --> 00:23:58.140
Jung Suk Hee.

00:23:59.140 --> 00:24:00.740
She looked like Jung Suk Hee.

00:24:01.650 --> 00:24:02.810
No.

00:24:03.610 --> 00:24:07.020
Jung Suk Hee died back then.
They told me she was dead for sure.

00:24:07.880 --> 00:24:09.190
There's no way she's still alive.

00:24:10.290 --> 00:24:11.520
It must be someone else
with the same name.

00:24:25.800 --> 00:24:26.840
Is something the matter?

00:24:28.310 --> 00:24:32.380
Kang Hyuk.
You told me Jung Suk Hee was dead, right?

00:24:32.710 --> 00:24:34.340
Pardon? Jung Suk Hee?

00:24:36.310 --> 00:24:39.080
- Why bring her up all of a sudden?
- Just answer me. I'm asking you.

00:24:39.880 --> 00:24:43.190
You said she was dead.
Or rather, she is dead, right?

00:24:44.550 --> 00:24:45.890
She fell from so high up.

00:24:45.890 --> 00:24:47.920
- There's no way she could've survived.
- What about the body?

00:24:48.120 --> 00:24:49.590
But her body was never found.

00:24:49.590 --> 00:24:51.900
The fact that nothing's happened
all this time must mean she's dead.

00:24:52.300 --> 00:24:55.930
Otherwise, the police
would have come straight to you.

00:24:56.300 --> 00:24:57.730
Do you think she would've stayed quiet?

00:24:58.240 --> 00:24:59.570
Not after her child was taken from her.

00:25:00.640 --> 00:25:03.340
But what brought this on all of a sudden?

00:25:03.870 --> 00:25:04.880
Right.

00:25:05.880 --> 00:25:07.080
It must just be someone
with the same name.

00:25:07.880 --> 00:25:09.550
Jung Suk Hee is a pretty common name.

00:25:10.310 --> 00:25:11.510
It's been so long.

00:25:12.120 --> 00:25:14.120
How would I even recognize her
after all this time?

00:25:14.180 --> 00:25:17.020
Did you happen to run into her?

00:25:17.350 --> 00:25:20.390
I feel uneasy.
I don't know why I feel so on edge.

00:25:21.290 --> 00:25:23.130
The fact that they never found a body
is unsettling,

00:25:23.530 --> 00:25:26.460
and hearing her exact name out of the blue
is unsettling too.

00:25:26.660 --> 00:25:29.870
Why did I have to see a woman
who looks like her? Just why?

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:33.500
I can't let this go.

00:25:33.970 --> 00:25:35.970
I need to return to where I last saw her.

00:25:40.010 --> 00:25:41.080
CEO Chae.

00:25:42.350 --> 00:25:43.350
What is it?

00:25:45.120 --> 00:25:46.320
The guy who was singing yesterday?

00:25:46.580 --> 00:25:48.390
You mean Oh Tae Pyung.

00:25:50.390 --> 00:25:52.220
Of course, I don't know where he lives.

00:26:04.300 --> 00:26:05.370
Yes, sir.

00:26:06.240 --> 00:26:08.470
What? You want me to come to the office?

00:26:19.580 --> 00:26:20.950
(Dream Group Negotiating
One Billion-dollar Investment...)

00:26:20.950 --> 00:26:22.290
(with a Middle Eastern
Sovereign Wealth Fund)

00:26:23.750 --> 00:26:26.720
Thankfully, it seems Seo Rin's photo
was well blocked in the articles.

00:26:27.920 --> 00:26:28.930
Okay.

00:26:29.860 --> 00:26:30.890
Of course.

00:26:31.530 --> 00:26:32.560
Okay.

00:26:33.300 --> 00:26:35.570
Yes. Right. I get it.

00:26:36.570 --> 00:26:40.600
Mom, hang on. What? Bring my resume?

00:26:41.240 --> 00:26:42.540
Okay. Got it.

00:26:58.390 --> 00:26:59.620
Jung Suk Hee?

00:27:47.400 --> 00:27:48.810
(The First Man)

00:27:48.810 --> 00:27:50.610
That was definitely Jung Suk Hee's face.

00:27:51.540 --> 00:27:53.140
I have to make sure.

00:27:53.440 --> 00:27:55.910
Bring your family relation certificate.
Make sure you do!

00:27:56.250 --> 00:27:59.650
If this tastes bad,
you have to go out with me. Deal?

00:27:59.850 --> 00:28:02.850
And if it's good,
don't you ever say that to me again.

00:28:03.450 --> 00:28:05.090
What happened to my angel?

00:28:05.520 --> 00:28:06.690
Hey!

00:28:06.690 --> 00:28:08.690
What kind of a guitar costs
over 3,000 dollars?

00:28:08.790 --> 00:28:11.760
- Settle in court, or do I press charges?
- What am I supposed to do?

00:28:11.960 --> 00:28:15.170
If it's truly Jung Suk Hee, there's no way
she would've stayed quiet until now.

00:28:15.970 --> 00:28:17.930
Once I confirm it with my own two eyes,

00:28:18.440 --> 00:28:20.000
then it will all make sense.